.18.0.post9+e462414">PMC11303214</a> | doi： <a href=https://doi.org/10.3389/fimmu.2024.1406929>10.3389/fimmu.2024.1406929</a></p></div> ]]>;</content:encoded><guid ispermalink="false"> PubMed：39114655</guid><pubDate> Thu, 08 Aug 2024 06:00:00 -0400</pubDate><dc:creator> Karen J Gonzalez</dc:creator><dc:creator>凯文·伊姆</dc:creator><dc:creator>Jorge CG Blanco</dc:creator><dc:creator> Marina S Boukhvalova</dc:creator><dc:creator> Eva-Maria Strauch</dc:creator><dc:date> 2024-08-08</dc:date><dc:source>免疫学前沿</dc:source><dc:title>系统的计算机辅助二硫键设计是稳定预融合I类融合蛋白的一般策略</dc:title><dc:identifier>PMID：39114655</dc:identifier><dc:identifier> PMC：PMC11303214</dc:identifier><dc:identifier> doi：10.3389/fimmu.2024.1406929</dc:identifier></item></channel></rss>